I haven't found too many JUnit resources in hard copy, but I also haven't
dug too deeply. The one hard copy reference I found, was in Martin Fowlers
book titled "Refactoring".

If memory serves, it contains one full chapter on unit testing w/ JUnit.

HTH,
Levi Cook
